{"word":"ἄμπυξ","slug":"ἄμπυξ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄμπυξ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ἀμπί</el>, aeolic for <a href='S:ἀμφί'><el>ἀμφί</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a woman's head-band, snood</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>anything circular, a wheel</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}